{"tid":2192871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現呀妹好似墮入網上情緣陷阱....","createTime":"2020-09-07T11:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:44:30.000Z","uid":68626,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"171f9b59f77bb5edb2b11354d982eedb2a7e09e5","tid":2192871,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我呀妹本身得中三學歷，今年都二十八了<br />\n講真個樣又真係唔靚，呢個世界對樣衰既人係好唔友善的。相信大家都知。<br />\n呢排佢好似癲左咁成日玩交友apps<br />\n有時係到陰陰咀笑，唔知笑乜。<br />\n好啦，呢排就開始黎料，我呀妹學歷唔高，唔係識好多英文。呢排成日無啦啦問我 colleague 係咪解學校咁樣解，又問我 military 係咪即係牛奶工廠。<br />\n講真，佢英文都唔識多幾隻，呢排係咁對住個apps打英文(我偷睇)，又見到佢問我咩 伊朗係咪被制裁國家(呀呢樣佢又識架喎)，可以點匯款過去。<br />\n<br />\n我依加都唔知點開口同佢講好，我地交情其實唔係咁好，作為呀哥...睇住佢仆街又唔係，都唔知點搞好...."},{"pid":"7988899d247f3ae37dbd21a2f91e547fdc1b1c5a","tid":2192871,"uid":180168,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"擺明呃錢啦"},{"pid":"976ceda1cc0792250d490ead4a7420c3233ac2c2","tid":2192871,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"直接同佢講比人呃囉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上大把新聞啦"},{"pid":"ccb95b119db65e4b39dd364f3f51482c393e9819","tid":2192871,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網求其搵都搵到案例啦 直接俾佢睇"},{"pid":"aa21634781f0ba85136c0b64024602afb7eeb076","tid":2192871,"uid":9392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"唔好理佢 一定要睇住佢仆街"},{"pid":"cc43b23d0cadb7aa76fcd6027069a235721f3ab4","tid":2192871,"uid":343964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:48:20.000Z","msg":"矛4甘的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f605cb0d3de2f1c7a8adc8a01edf614197221f1","tid":2192871,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccb95b119db65e4b39dd364f3f51482c393e9819","tid":2192871,"uid":153781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB